file.string: Maths and English Personalized Learning App

A grade 1 student should know: 
MATHS :
 1. Addition up to 2-digit numbers.
2. Subtraction up to 2-digit 
 numbers.
3. Multiplication Tables till Table of 
 10.
ENGLISH :
1. Vocabulary -> Bathroom, Body
 parts, Colors, Animals, Fruits,
 Vegetables and opposites.
2. Spelling -> Most common words, 3-letter and 4-letter words.

A grade 2 student should know:
1.Addition upto 3-digits.
 2.Subtraction upto 3-digits.
 3.Multiplying of 2-digit
and tables up to 12.
 4.Division of numbers upto 20

A grade 3 student should know:
1.Addition upto 5-digits.
 2.Subtraction upto 5-digits.
 3.Multiplying of 2-digit
and tables up to 15.
 4.Division of numbers upto 20
Vocabulary -> Bathroom, Body parts, Colors, Animals, Fruits, Vegetables and opposites.
Spelling -> Most common words, 3-letter and 4-letter words.
Vocabulary -> Clothes, Feelings, Insects, Kitchen, Living room, days of the week, months of the year.
Spelling -> Essential words, Most common words, Short vowel sound words.
Multiplication of 2-digit with 1-digit, 3-digit with 1-digit and 2-digit with 2-digit.
Vocabulary-> School, Summer, Town, Transport, Weather, Professions.
Spelling -> Essential words, Most common words, Compound words, Long and Short vowels, Words with double letter after short vowels, Words with double vowels.
